Changelog:
---------
2006/08/31 version 1.0.0 Initial version by Oliver Riesen (oliver@riesen.org)

2006/12/15 version 1.1.0 by Oliver Riesen (oliver@riesen.org)
- Language Support Module offers various translations for: "Buddy" (Freund/
  Freundin, Kollege/Kollegin, Kumpel/Bekannte) and "Sticky" (Festgepinnt,
  Pickert [österr.][ugs.], Wichtig).
- Standard and extended format for email notifications.

2008/04/18 version 1.2.0 by Oliver Riesen (oliver@riesen.org)
- Rewrite for Phorum 5.2.
- Additional translation for "buddy": Kontakt.

2015/08/04 version 1.2.1 by Oliver Riesen (oliver@riesen.org)
- Update for Google Maps Module 2.0.6

2016/04/20 version 1.2.2 by Oliver Riesen-Mallmann (oliver@riesen.org)
- Obsolete assignment by reference (&new) removed; see:
  http://www.phorum.org/phorum5/read.php?61,156894,157057#msg-157057;
  thanks to Fabian Bastin (http://www.phorum.org/phorum5/profile.php?61,3024).